title: For Sale:  BEWARE!!!! Fake Trijicon RMR's!!!!
postcontent:
Just a friendly heads up to everyone out there looking for a Trijicon RMR. There has recently been a few Phony/knockoff/airsoft  RMR's floating around armslist. Most of the fakes will be pretty easy to spot, here's what to look for:

No ® after the trijicon logo on the left side
Most are supposed RM06 models
All have the same fake serial number---- 080782
Hex adjustment screw, the real RMR's have slotted adjustment screws

To check legitimacy of the optic contact trijicon directly here:
http://www.trijicon.com/na_en/support/product_authenticity.php

Guys if it sounds too good to be true, then it probably is. Have a good day folks.
